msgid "Dozens of books are neatly organized on the shelves."
msgstr "大量の本が棚にきちんと整理されている。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Library_Doorknob.misc_books_1.choice"
msgid "An untitled book stands out. Read a passage?"
msgstr "無題の本が目を惹いた。一節を読む？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Library_Doorknob.misc_books_1.choice.An untitled book stands out. Read a passage?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "読む"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Library_Doorknob.misc_books_1.choice.An untitled book stands out. Read a passage?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "読まない"

msgid "Variations of rituals ______carefully documented ______ recipient."
msgstr "様々な儀式は受容者______入念に記録______。"

msgid "Any human that enters ______ by way of a ritual is carefully tracked."
msgstr "儀式によって______に入る人間は入念に追跡されている。"

msgid "No accounts of humans infiltrating by their own means exist, _________ easily detected."
msgstr "独自の方法で侵入した人間の報告は存在せず、_________容易に検知される。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Library_Doorknob.misc_books_2.choice"
msgid "An untitled book stands out. Read a passage?"
msgstr "無題の本が目を惹いた。一節を読む？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Library_Doorknob.misc_books_2.choice.An untitled book stands out. Read a passage?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "読む"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Library_Doorknob.misc_books_2.choice.An untitled book stands out. Read a passage?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "読まない"

msgid "Average recorded survival time of humans following ritual rules: 15 minutes."
msgstr "儀式のルールに従った人間の平均生存記録: 15分。"

msgid "Average survival time ________ breaching ritual rules: 140 minutes."
msgstr "儀式のルールを破った________平均生存記録: 140分。"

msgid "Average rate of adherence to the ritual rules: 98.31%"
msgstr "儀式のルールへの平均準拠率: 98.31％"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Library_Doorknob.misc_books_3.choice"
msgid "An untitled book stands out. Read a passage?"
msgstr "無題の本が目を惹いた。一節を読む？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Library_Doorknob.misc_books_3.choice.An untitled book stands out. Read a passage?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "読む"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Library_Doorknob.misc_books_3.choice.An untitled book stands out. Read a passage?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "読まない"

msgid "Demons can pick up on a human's soul from at least five meters away."
msgstr "妖魔は最低でも5メートルの距離から人間の魂を感知できる。"

msgid "Exceptions exist ___________ as well as the elderly or the sick; they are less perceivable and less satiating."
msgstr "例外はあり、___________や老人、病人がそれである。そうした人間は感知しづらく、満足も得づらい。"

msgid "Due to these factors, their value is considered to be negligible."
msgstr "それらの要素から、そうした人間の価値は些末と考えられている。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Library_Doorknob.misc_books_4.choice"
msgid "An untitled book stands out. Read a passage?"
msgstr "無題の本が目を惹いた。一節を読む？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Library_Doorknob.misc_books_4.choice.An untitled book stands out. Read a passage?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "読む"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Library_Doorknob.misc_books_4.choice.An untitled book stands out. Read a passage?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "読まない"

msgid "Demons won't hesitate to kill and consume ______"
msgstr "妖魔は______を殺し、消費することを躊躇しない。"

msgid "_____'s regulations don't allow free consumption of souls ________ must be reported."
msgstr "_____の規則では魂の自由な消費は許可されておらず、________は報告されねばならない。"

msgid "Any demand ________ through the appropriate channels."
msgstr "需要は全て、適切な経路を通じて________。"

msgid "White grass is growing on the floor. It's soft to the touch."
msgstr "白い草が床に育っている。触れると柔らかい。"

msgid "You can spot some faint shapes in the window."
msgstr "窓にはかすかな形がいくつか見える。"
